OL,3,CStroud Lido: Flashmob forms for
OL,4,Ccampaign to reopen pool
OL,6,FHundreds of Stroud Lido campaigners
OL,7,Fheld a flashmob in the town centre
OL,8,Fthis weekend, urging the council to
OL,9,Freopen the outdoor pool.
OL,11,FIt comes ahead of a council debate
OL,12,Fthis week on the future of the open-
OL,13,Fair swimming pool.
OL,15,FThe pool at Stratford Park Lido, which
OL,16,Ffirst opened in 1937, was shut over
OL,17,Fsafety concerns - with council bosses
OL,18,Festimating around #5 million is needed
OL,19,Fto upgrade the site.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
