PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776077823
OL,3,CStroud Lido: Flashmob forms for
OL,4,Ccampaign to reopen pool
OL,6,FThe closure has led to anger from many
OL,7,Ffrustrated locals.
OL,9,FWhy was the pool closed?
OL,11,FA risk assessment conducted in
OL,12,FFebruary this year found three major
OL,13,Fhazards at the site.
OL,15,FThese include multiple cracks formed
OL,16,Fthrough the concrete on the poolside
OL,17,Fdirectly beneath and next to the
OL,18,Fdiving board, indicating instability
OL,19,Fas well as concerns that this is
OL,20,Frelated to the iron pipework or pool
OL,21,Ftank condition.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776077823
OL,3,CStroud Lido: Flashmob forms for
OL,4,Ccampaign to reopen pool
OL,6,FThe survey also found excessive
OL,7,Fcorrosion in the pipework and the pool
OL,8,Ftank.
OL,10,FWhat are the options for the pool?
OL,12,FCouncillors will consider investment
OL,13,Foptions for the lido at the strategy
OL,14,Fand resources committee meeting at
OL,15,FEbley Mill on April 16.
OL,17,FOption 1: One option includes doing
OL,18,Fthe minimum recommended works needed
OL,19,Fto keep the 50m pool operational.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776077823
OL,3,CStroud Lido: Flashmob forms for
OL,4,Ccampaign to reopen pool
OL,6,FThis would involve replacing ageing
OL,7,Fpipework with modern PVC pipework,
OL,8,Finstalling a new filtration system,
OL,9,Fand renewing heating and plant
OL,10,Fequipment to improve reliability and
OL,11,Fefficiency. The main toddler pool
OL,12,Fwould be relined, with new ladders and
OL,13,Fpaving.
OL,15,FHowever, the report says it would also
OL,16,Fentail soft landscaping and reducing
OL,17,Fthe depth of the pool to 1.5m to
OL,18,Fsupport heat retention and improve
OL,19,Faccessibility.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776077823
OL,3,CStroud Lido: Flashmob forms for
OL,4,Ccampaign to reopen pool
OL,6,FThis scheme also introduces a pool
OL,7,Fhoist to improve access for people
OL,8,Fwith reduced mobility and is estimated
OL,9,Fto cost around #5.1m and potential
OL,10,Fincome could increase by #218,000.
OL,12,FTo complete the essential works,
OL,13,FStratford Park lido would need to stay
OL,14,Ffully closed until everything is
OL,15,Ffinished, which would take around a
OL,16,Fyear from awarding the works contract.
OL,18,FOption Two: The second option aims at
OL,19,Fproviding a better visitor experience
OL,20,Fwith operational improvements at the
OL,21,Flido.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
