FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776077823
OL,3,CStroud Lido: Flashmob forms for
OL,4,Ccampaign to reopen pool
OL,6,FIf taken forward, it would deliver all
OL,7,Fthe minimum recommended works as well
OL,8,Fas transforming the toddler pool into
OL,9,Fan inclusive splash pad, creating safe
OL,10,Fwater play for younger children.
OL,12,FThe disused canoe store would become a
OL,13,Fnew cafe, generating income and
OL,14,Fencouraging visitors to stay longer.
OL,16,FAnd extra soft landscaping would
OL,17,Freplace hard surfaces, improving the
OL,18,Fsite's appearance, drainage and
OL,19,Fbiodiversity.
OL,26,@uD@Hrr
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776077823
OL,3,CStroud Lido: Flashmob forms for
OL,4,Ccampaign to reopen pool
OL,6,FOfficers say this would create a more
OL,7,Ffamily friendly and appealing
OL,8,Fenvironment with stronger commercial
OL,9,Fpotential.
OL,11,FAnd it is estimated to cost #7.9m but
OL,12,Fhas the potential to increase income
OL,13,Fby #1.63m over the first five years.
OL,15,FOption Three: A third option would be
OL,16,Fto completely reimagine Stratford Park
OL,17,Flido as an outdoor wellness centre.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776077823
OL,3,CStroud Lido: Flashmob forms for
OL,4,Ccampaign to reopen pool
OL,6,FThis would deliver all of the
OL,7,Finfrastructure upgrades from the first
OL,8,Foption and many of the improvements of
OL,9,Fthe second option.
OL,11,FHowever, the paddling pool area would
OL,12,Fbecome a wellness garden featuring
OL,13,Fheat rooms, hydrotherapy, ice baths
OL,14,Fand relaxation spaces, and the
OL,15,Fexisting 50m pool would be replaced
OL,16,Fwith a more efficient heated 25m
OL,17,Fsingle depth pool.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776077823
OL,3,CStroud Lido: Flashmob forms for
OL,4,Ccampaign to reopen pool
OL,6,FA new large splash pad would be
OL,7,Fcreated in the freed-up space,
OL,8,Fsupported by a removable canopy for
OL,9,Fimproved year-round use, and major
OL,10,Flandscaping would introduce green
OL,11,Fareas throughout, creating a flagship
OL,12,Fsite for health, wellbeing, tourism
OL,13,Fand commercial sustainability.
OL,15,FThis option is estimated to cost #10m
OL,16,Fbut has the potential to increase
OL,17,Fincome by #2.7m.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
